Concatenation Streams






  Concatenation Streams allow multiple input sources to be combined into a singe source stream.



ConcatInputStream
Example
<pre>// Pre-pend data to a InputStream "in"
// giving a new stream.
in = new ConcatInputStream(
    new ByteArrayInputStream(
        new byte[]{
            3,1,4,1,5,9
        }
    ),
    in
);</pre>



