ConcatReader

Example
<pre>// Pre-pend data to a Reader "in"
// giving a new reader.
in = new ConcatReader(
    new StringReader(
        "Pre-pending this data."
    ),
    in
);
</pre>


  Combines multiple character stream sources into a single character stream.  
